🛠MRFIXITDIY Takeover!🛠 Hey everyone! I’m Aaron Massey from @mrfixitdiy and I’m a DIY Home Improvement Expert (if there is such a thing) and a Woodworker. Carhartt and I have teamed up once again this Holiday season to showcase some unique Holiday Gift build ideas ranging from the super simple DIY to the very involved woodworking projects. They’ve graciously allowed me to takeover their account for the day so I can take you behind the scenes of our latest collaboration and show you some of the fun stuff I’m working on. You can also win a few of the projects I’ve built as part of Carhartt’s 12 Days of Handmade Gifts! Follow along with me today here and on Instagram stories to see what I’m up to! #mrfixitdiy #mrfixitdiytakeover #carhartt #verymerryhomemadeholidays
